Source: magmakeys
Section: base
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Stefan Tomanek <stefan@pico.ruhr.de>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7)
Standards-Version: 3.8.1
Homepage: http://stefans.datenbruch.de/magmakeys/

Package: magmakeys
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, perl
Recommends: libnet-dbus-perl
Description: global, user and session independent hotkey daemon
  Magmakeys observes all connected input devices and launches
  configured commands when certain keys are pressed. The daemon
  works as a system wide service and is independent of any user
  session.
